DIAMOND FULL FASHIONED HOSIERY CO., Appellant, v. William LEADER et al., Appellees. No. 6568. Circuit Court of Appeals, Third Circuit Nov. 12, 1937. For opinion below see D.C., 20 F.Supp. 467. Ralph S. Croskey, of Philadelphia, Pa., for appellant. M. Herbert Syme, of Philadelphia, Pa., for appellees.

Before BUFFINGTON and BIGGS, Circuit Judges, and WATSON, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on agreement of counsel.
